            <corpname rules="aacr" source="local">
               <part>Yale University. Student Army Training Corps</part>
            </corpname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_e06e8b8d22f5fe53739ef115ab0397cd">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 42-A (YRG 42-A), Records of military training programs at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
